{"tid":1659931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"耿爽：两名美国人因涉嫌组织他人偷越边境被刑事拘留","createTime":"2019-10-17T08:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T08:19:08.000Z","uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"342ebc8ccbbbd98fb8d332467ec1000bcb49ad6e","tid":1659931,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:18:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnKniE5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.huanqiu.com%2Farticle%2F9CaKrnKniE5&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=cfd3d96b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnKniE5</a><br />\n<br />\n【环球时报-环球网报道 记者 李司坤】在17日下午举行的外交部例会上，有来自法新社的记者就两名美国人上个月在江苏被逮捕一事提问。对此，发言人耿爽回应说，经向有关部门了解，美国公民阿丽莎&middot;彼得森和雅各布&bull;哈兰因涉嫌组织他人偷越边境，于9月27日、29日被江苏省公安机关依法分别采取刑事拘留、取保候审强制措施。&ldquo;办案机关已经及时将有关情况通报了美国驻上海总领馆，安排美方领事官员进行领事探视，并依法保障两人的合法权益。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n随后，有路透社记者追问道，此事跟当前的中美关系是否有关?耿爽表示：&ldquo;我没有看出有什么具体的联系。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4ddb8ee6bed02417a879daba9f99b3d61f8e644c","tid":1659931,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:18:35.000Z","msg":"好小家啊真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759ea7fa85e279b04404fdae039b5d6e7dcd2480","tid":1659931,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}